definitions.definition: Aged urine , historically used by the Anglo-Saxons and others as fertilizer for high nitrogen content.

main_definition: Aged urine , historically used by the Anglo-Saxons and others as fertilizer for high nitrogen content.

definitions.definition: Any of several species of slender marine fishes of the genus Ammodytes , including the common European species ( Ammodytes tobianus ) and the American species ( Ammodytes americanus ).

main_definition: Any of several species of slender marine fishes of the genus Ammodytes , including the common European species ( Ammodytes tobianus ) and the American species ( Ammodytes americanus ).
